dc:description: Blue glass.  Rim appears to have been cut off.  Good material.  Milky weathering.  Iridescence and some golden-brown incrustation.  Blowing spirals.  Toilet bottle.  Tall, cylindrical neck which broadens out slightly toward base.  Triangular body.  Flat base.
Gazda: Toilet bottle. Glass, free blown.
